'''Yuma Sammang''' is the goddess of the [[Limbu]] community of [[Nepal]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.limbulibrary.com.np/pdf/HISTORY%20&%20CULTURE-Iman.pdf |title=History of the Kirat People |publisher=Limbulibrary.com.np |accessdate=2013-09-01}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=S07zMmQuhjoC&pg=PA317&lpg=PA317&dq=Yuma+Sammang&source=bl&ots=QUZgC0X8Qg&sig=bcEFtZgRK4Evp4-ekB-H6Cn6pAM&hl=en&sa=X&ei=kvWEUbzhCKT_iAeox4DYBg&ved=0CEsQ6AEwBg |title=Mythology of the People of Sikkim - J. R. Subba - Google Books |publisher=Books.google.com.au |date= |accessdate=2013-09-01}}</ref>

